'''Kostbera''' is the wife of the mythical Norse hero [[Hagen|Hogni]]. She is mentioned in [[Atlamál]]. With Hogni they are the parents of four sons: Solar, Snævar, Hniflung and Gjuki. Gjuki is only mentioned in [[Drap Niflunga]].

